XIME<ref>{{cite web | url=https://github.com/stackia/XIME | title=XIME Input Method Editor - Yet another Rime Frontend for Mac OS X | publisher=Github | accessdate=2015-04-16 | archive-date=2019-02-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220194624/https://github.com/stackia/XIME | dead-url=no }}</ref>是由Stackie Jia創作的基於Rime引擎的[[macOS|macOS]]輸入法。
